summary: A sword I made and am proud of, It is one of my first and my texturing skills aren't all that great at this point.
descriptionHtml: My very first successful creation from blender to nifskope to skyrim. I am finally aquiring the skill in both blender and nifskope to do some successful modding so expect more and cleaner mods from me in the future. Mainly weapons and armor. Sword is in barrel in whiterun behind olava the feebles house. See pictures for details
author: Chris5910
